<br />
<br />There is accomodation for non-stock stuff in NSF format though, like the play speed if someone wants to do 30hz, 120hz, or whatever.  It's just not used often or at all.  I've only ever seen a couple NSFs use 30hz (I think 720Â° and Chase HQ).

		

